      Compute the Tanimoto Similarity (also known as Jaccard Index or Jaccard Similarity Coefficient) which measures how similar this Fingerprint is compared to the other given Fingerprint except the method will short circuit and return OptionalDouble.empty() if this fingerprint logical and'ed to the other fingerprint don't have the same value.
